/home/rb/AI/first-router/launch.sh

그 다음
curl http://127.0.0.1:8090/route \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d @/home/rb/AI/first-router/examples/local_general_router_request.json

로컬 답변까지 같이 보고 싶으면
curl http://127.0.0.1:8090/handle \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d @/home/rb/AI/first-router/examples/local_general_router_request.json


